        "filename": "logdog/appengine/coordinator/endpoints/services/scheduleArchiveTask.go",
        "patchSetId": 7
      },
      "lineNbr": 74,
      "author": {
        "id": 1002080
      },
      "writtenOn": "2018-12-15T00:21:58Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Can\u0027t run this mutation immediately since it\u0027s a delayed mutation.  Took your suggestion in the other thread to always swap out the archive key though, which should solve this problem.",
      "parentUuid": "214bdb68_3ef951eb",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 74,
        "startChar": 24,
